{"about_the_game":"<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/spr_spica_buckler.gif?t=1734799264\" /><br><strong>Virgo Versus the Zodiac is a sci-fi/fantasy JRPG inspired by the Mario &amp; Luigi RPG series and the Mother RPG series</strong> in which you play as an obsessed villain.<br><br>The game features traditional turn-based combat with real-time execution of moves: blocking, countering and timing your attacks carefully as well as predicting your foes' moves is essential to succeed in <strong>Virgo\u2019s twisted and unforgiving cosmic quest to bring back the Golden Age</strong>, a period of peace, symmetry and balance, or so she thinks.<br><br>In this galaxy where every action means a reaction, you\u2019ll play as Virgo, the Holy Queen, often called Dreadful Queen by heretics, bringing mayhem to the Zodiac Realms and leaving a trail of stardust on the way, all to fit her excessively righteous worldview.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/features.png?t=1734799264\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>     <u><strong>A unique turn based combat system</strong> featuring <strong>timed-actions and counterattacks</strong> that favors a balance of offense and defense, rewarding a deliberate mind and swift fingers.</u><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/Battle_en.gif?t=1734799264\" /><br></li><li>     <u><strong>No Random Encounters:</strong> Every fight is a unique challenge designed specifically for you.</u><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/Encounter_en.gif?t=1734799264\" /><br></li><li>     <strong>A focus on exploration with multiple endings:</strong> There are many people, places, and items to see among the stars, and each interaction could be the one that determines your fate!<br></li><li>     <strong>Zodiac Memories:</strong> Peer behind the veil to explore the backstories of the Zodiacs!<br></li><li>     <u><strong>Take the Dangerous Route</strong> and fight off the Space Reptiles in an optional Action Filled Shoot'em Up Minigame!</u><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/Shoot__em_up_en.gif?t=1734799264\" /><br></li><li>     <u>And most importantly: <strong>Riding Alpacas!</strong></u><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/Alpaca_Riding.gif?t=1734799264\" /></li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/920320/extras/spr_frans_idle.gif?t=1734799264\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fate is Upon Us ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/28ed90304f741e972058b4f4235a37bf3e9ce1bd.jpg"},{"name":"Party Rock","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/850a6adc363aea165fa3925c832ada61acec813b.jpg"},{"name":"Cow of Duty","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/45680f46a7398c4b36bf0dfb91652d48f5839d8c.jpg"},{"name":"Mood Breaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/889de1dcf0882eaa52c6b79561d79730a019d278.jpg"},{"name":"High High High High High High High","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/2f258b89f7028d58614a82146c4ed7b1bdb86279.jpg"},{"name":"Cookie Crisis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/ee8da41b35a18a7b2dc7a3c77d0189084dae3771.jpg"},{"name":"Persistence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/920320/aee1fd717351e8158b49f4ab25be1df55e7589dd.jpg"},{"name":"Capritalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s